1 run script
 
  clean.sh

first to clean all old files

2 run script

  bootstrap.sh

to make use of GNU autoconf+automake

3 run 

./configure --prefix=$HOME/MCF/mcf/mcf_install/ FC=ifort MPIFC=mpif90
LDFLAGS=-L$HOME/MCF/ppm/local/lib/ FCFLAGS=-I$HOME/MCF/ppm/local/include/
MAKEDEPF90=$HOME/MCF/ppm/local/bin/makedepf90 

to generate Makefile

4 run 

  make -j 8

to compile mcf code.


